          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.In the Case of the Radiochemical Method,",
                "A Measurement of the Amount of Be-10 Formed in a Given",
                "Irradiation is Difficult Due to the Fact That the",
                "Activity of the Short-Lived Be-7 (HALF-LIFE=53.6 D)",
                "Interferes with the Measurements of the B-Activity",
                "Of Be-10 (E(MAX)=0.55 MEV), the Interference is",
                "Appreciable in Spite of the Fact That Be-7 is a Gamma-",
                "Emitter. Therefore, It Becomes Necessary to Wait For",
                "Several Years After an Irradiation to Allow the Be-7",
                "Activity to Decay to a Level Where Its Presence Does",
                "Not Contribute any Significant Counting in the",
                "B-Counter Employed For Detection of Be-10."
              ]
            }
          ],
